{"tid":550602,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港地震！天文台接報告：震動持續數秒","createTime":"2018-02-05T01:56:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-05T04:40:09.000Z","uid":152123,"like":4,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e8740127296d6890176e3be5900007334cc737c7","tid":550602,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T01:56:10.000Z","msg":"台灣花蓮昨晚9時12分起，接連發生21次地震，今天凌晨零時8分及零時54分，又先後發生黎克特制3.5級及4.4級地震，震央均在花蓮近海，當地人一夜難眠。直至今晨5時，台灣兩日以來共發生50次地震。而昨晚最強一次地震，已由5.8級修訂為6.1級。<br />\n<br />\n本港天文台今日凌晨發佈消息，表示也錄得台灣昨晚9時57發生黎克特制6級地震，初步分析，震中位於北緯24.20度，東經121.70度附近，即花蓮之東北偏北約20公里。<br />\n<br />\n此外，天文台接獲數名市民報告，表示感到輕微震動，震動維持數秒。初步分析顯示本港的地震烈度為修訂麥加利地震烈度表的第II (二)度，即在樓宇上層或合適位置，且在靜止中的人有感。"},{"pid":"600cd0dea3c0095b715ce5871c523cf8ea8dc357","tid":550602,"uid":152123,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T01:57:10.000Z","msg":"地震可唔可以射波<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ee20a4a7435829152ff37ff224dd26ae3429dfa","tid":550602,"uid":48,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"600cd0dea3c0095b715ce5871c523cf8ea8dc357","tid":550602,"uid":152123,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T01:57:10.000Z","msg":"地震可唔可以射波<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T01:58:31.000Z","msg":"9級都要番工"},{"pid":"756bb5b7a4430d039c15ded89c6cf7d0e480f3ee","tid":550602,"uid":69013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T01:59:29.000Z","msg":"次次都feel唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fc0ea1acc20b92c7ca38325b9bb53193457f3a7","tid":550602,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ee20a4a7435829152ff37ff224dd26ae3429dfa","tid":550602,"uid":48,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"600cd0dea3c0095b715ce5871c523cf8ea8dc357","tid":550602,"uid":152123,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T01:57:10.000Z","msg":"地震可唔可以射波<img src=\"/as